--How to run the Code
./run.sh

-- Implementation

fetchdata.py - Converts the documents into Vectors using bag of words approach by removing stopwords and stem them. 

documentclassifier.py- Determines the Tfidf matrix and applies classification algorithms on them

documentcluster.py - Determines the Tfidf matrix and applies clustering algorithm on them.


